Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:56.20,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(79,135)\fs21\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(495,0)}迷人的先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道這附近有沒有哪家店的茶比較好喝的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 有一家店不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 請務必帶我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.75,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(163,82)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}想著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.75,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(105,155)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}他是從哪裏來的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬社長 走…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這身奇怪的打扮是要幹嘛啊…亞利亞社長
