Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.03,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(145,147)\fs21\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}我…我不是你說的那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 你是要幫我忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才參加那邊的馬戲團表演時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心就讓球散得一地都是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是幫了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧 亞利亞社長？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？這隻貓是怎麼搞的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯 不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 在那邊保持平衡站好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把球撿回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 全撿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就再試一次看看吧 不要輸給那隻貓了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.41,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(516,124)\fs22\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(0,1200)}把人偶弄髒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:12.52,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(255,60)\fs40\t(0,1356,1,\fs30)}不及格的英雄! !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法啊 掉到哪裏去了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 我要去找啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不要去了 已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰幫忙拿回來的呢？而且…變得好髒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 就算髒也沒關係 小健回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是神把他帶回來的 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:22:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 我不會再丟下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:13.18,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(576,193)\fs20\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(450,1400)}那一天的夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:13.18,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(90,234)\fs18\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(660,1400)}感覺是在所有的夕陽之中 ——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:19.62,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(186,239)\fs18\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(300,0)}看起來最耀眼的。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.33,0:22:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏 說不定亞利亞社長真的是個英雄哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:46.58,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(431,329)\fs35\c&H50F654&\fad(1350,0)}那位 帥氣的英雄啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:46.58,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(477,473)\fs30\fad(1350,0)}結束
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.89,0:24:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想見 好想見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想見到她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.70,0:24:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個快一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要先走一步了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.57,0:24:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.53,0:24:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位 星星一般的精靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.17,0:24:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們一起度過美好的時光吧
