Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:01:06.38,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 融入身體裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:17.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}閉上雙眼 看到的
